text: ITTF World Tour 2017 German Open, Gerassimenko Kirill Kirill Gerassimenko (born 18 December 1996) is a Kazakhstani table tennis player. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's singles event, in which he was eliminated in the first round by Ádám Pattantyús. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani male table tennis players Category:Olympic table tennis players of Kazakhstan Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Table tennis players at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Kazakhstan
